|_{sp} < 1. In Gl(n)+ this set\nis geodesically convex for every unitarily invariant norm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 7 Jul 2019 23:47:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-09"}
