planet systems and stars\nin need of longer radial velocity and photometric follow-up than those already\nperformed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Jul 2019 01:29:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Oct 2019 02:29:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-24"}
